channel.title: Would anyone want to join me?
channel.description: Hello, I'm not really sure where to put this, but I have quit the RSPS community for the past year due to the decline of "fun servers." I cannot stand all the TrisidiaX based servers, and 600+ Cache servers. In terms of this, I recovered a old source from I weed I he had posted in the downloads, and began to make it my own. I have done so many fun things with it, which I won't give details about, But I plan to put it on a VPS sometime in the coming weeks, and was wondering if anyone wanted to login and have some fun with me, just messing around, reliving the good days of servers.
